# Worker Loop: catalog-loop

Parent: `llm-wiki-mission-loop`

## Goal

Keep offline catalog generation and listing short-path aligned with docs 14–16.

## Read before touching code

1. `docs/refactor-mcp/14-implementation-plan.zh.md`
2. `docs/refactor-mcp/15-verification-plan.zh.md`
3. `docs/refactor-mcp/16-decision-scope-all-A.zh.md`
4. `state/phase.md`

## Iterate

1. State which phase gate (G0–G3) or catalog invariant is at risk.
2. Make the smallest change; one primary variable per PR.
3. Verify:

```bash
npm run typecheck
npm test -- tests/catalog-extract
npm run catalog:gen
```

4. When listing path changes: run `npm run verify:listing` if `DEEPSEEK_API_KEY` available; else inbox.

## Stop signals

Use `blocked-needs-credential` when E0/E1 requires API key unavailable.
Use `done` when gate commands for the touched phase pass.
